{"id": "art-149", "label": "Art. 149", "title": "Art. 149: Măsurile de protecţie a investigatorilor sub acoperire şi a colaboratorilor", "slug": "art-149", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1226134984\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2423\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1226134984\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 149:\nM&#259;surile de protec&#355;ie a investigatorilor sub acoperire &#351;i a\ncolaboratorilor </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1527841289\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2422\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1527841289\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Identitatea real&#259; a investigatorilor sub acoperire\n&#351;i a colaboratorilor cu o alt&#259; identitate decât cea real&#259; nu\npoate fi dezv&#259;luit&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_700198529\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2421\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_700198529\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Procurorul, judec&#259;torul de drepturi &#351;i\nlibert&#259;&#355;i, judec&#259;torul de camer&#259; preliminar&#259; sau\ninstan&#355;a de judecat&#259; are dreptul de a cunoa&#351;te adev&#259;rata\nidentitate a investigatorului sub acoperire &#351;i a colaboratorului, cu\nrespectarea secretului profesional.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1364477147\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2420\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1364477147\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Investigatorul sub acoperire, colaboratorul,\ninformatorul, precum &#351;i membrii de familie ai acestora sau alte persoane\nsupuse amenin&#355;&#259;rilor, intimid&#259;rilor sau actelor de\nviolen&#355;&#259;, în leg&#259;tur&#259; cu activitatea desf&#259;&#351;urat&#259;\nde investigatorul sub acoperire, informator sau colaborator, pot beneficia de\nm&#259;suri specifice de protec&#355;ie a martorilor, potrivit legii.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}